select.id: get給付実績情報

mapper.select: SELECT DbT3017."hiHokenshaNo", DbT3017."serviceTeikyoYM", DbT3017."seiriNo", DbT3017."kyufuSakuseiKubunCode", DbT3017."jigyoshoNo", shikibetsuNoA."shikibetsuNo", shikibetsuNoA."shikibetsuNo" || ' ' || shikibetsuNoA."ryakusho" AS shikibetsuMeisho FROM rgdb."DbT3017KyufujissekiKihon" AS DbT3017 LEFT JOIN (SELECT "shikibetsuNo", "ryakusho", rank_number FROM (SELECT T3118."shikibetsuNo", T3118."ryakusho", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY T3118."shikibetsuNo" ORDER BY T3118."tekiyoKaishiYM"DESC, T3118."tekiyoShuryoYM" DESC) AS rank_number FROM rgdb."DbT3118ShikibetsuNoKanri" AS T3118 WHERE T3118."isDeleted" = FALSE AND T3118."tekiyoKaishiYM" <= #{サービス提供年月} AND (T3118."tekiyoShuryoYM" IS NULL OR ( T3118."tekiyoShuryoYM" IS NOT NULL AND #{サービス提供年月} <= T3118."tekiyoShuryoYM")) ) AS T1 WHERE T1.rank_number = 1 ) AS shikibetsuNoA ON DbT3017."inputShikibetsuNo" = shikibetsuNoA."shikibetsuNo" WHERE DbT3017."isDeleted" = FALSE AND DbT3017."hokenshaHoyuKyufujissekiJohoSakujoFlag" = FALSE AND DbT3017."serviceTeikyoYM" = #{サービス提供年月} AND DbT3017."hiHokenshaNo" = #{被保険者番号} AND DbT3017."seiriNo" = #{整理番号} AND DbT3017."inputShikibetsuNo" = #{識別番号} ORDER BY DbT3017."toshiNo" DESC

FROM rgdb."DbT7060KaigoJigyosha" WHERE rgdb."DbT7060KaigoJigyosha"."isDeleted" = FALSE AND rgdb."DbT7060KaigoJigyosha"."jigyoshaNo" = #{事業所番号} AND (((SUBSTR(rgdb."DbT7060KaigoJigyosha"."yukoKaishiYMD", 1, 6) <= #{サービス提供年月}) AND (#{サービス提供年月} <= SUBSTR(rgdb."DbT7060KaigoJigyosha"."yukoShuryoYMD", 1, 6))) OR ((SUBSTR(rgdb."DbT7060KaigoJigyosha"."yukoKaishiYMD", 1, 6) <= #{サービス提供年月}) AND (rgdb."DbT7060KaigoJigyosha"."yukoShuryoYMD" IS NULL OR rgdb."DbT7060KaigoJigyosha"."yukoShuryoYMD" = '')))

select.id: get識別番号管理データ

mapper.select:
SELECT * FROM ( SELECT ,
FROM rgdb."DbT3017KyufujissekiKihon" AS "DbT3017KyufujissekiKihon", rgdb."DbT3033KyufujissekiShukei" AS "DbT3033KyufujissekiShukei" WHERE "DbT3033KyufujissekiShukei"."inputShikibetsuNo" NOT IN('3411') AND "DbT3033KyufujissekiShukei"."hiHokenshaNo" = #{被保険者番号} AND #{サービス提供年月_開始} <= "DbT3033KyufujissekiShukei"."serviceTeikyoYM" AND "DbT3033KyufujissekiShukei"."serviceTeikyoYM" <= #{サービス提供年月_終了} AND "DbT3033KyufujissekiShukei"."inputShikibetsuNo" = "DbT3017KyufujissekiKihon"."inputShikibetsuNo" AND "DbT3017KyufujissekiKihon"."kyufuSakuseiKubunCode" IN('1', '2') AND "DbT3033KyufujissekiShukei"."hiHokenshaNo" = "DbT3017KyufujissekiKihon"."hiHokenshaNo" AND "DbT3017KyufujissekiKihon"."kyufuJissekiKubunCode" IN('1', '2') AND "DbT3033KyufujissekiShukei"."jigyoshoNo" = "DbT3017KyufujissekiKihon"."jigyoshoNo" AND "DbT3033KyufujissekiShukei"."seiriNo" = "DbT3017KyufujissekiKihon"."seiriNo" ) AS A WHERE A."dbT3033KyufujissekiShukei_shinsaYM" = (SELECT MAX("shinsaYM") AS "shinsaYM" FROM rgdb."DbT3033KyufujissekiShukei" AS DbT3033KyufujissekiShukei WHERE DbT3033KyufujissekiShukei."inputShikibetsuNo" = A."dbT3033KyufujissekiShukei_inputShikibetsuNo" AND DbT3033KyufujissekiShukei."hiHokenshaNo" = A."dbT3033KyufujissekiShukei_hiHokenshaNo" AND DbT3033KyufujissekiShukei."serviceTeikyoYM" = A."dbT3033KyufujissekiShukei_serviceTeikyoYM" AND DbT3033KyufujissekiShukei."serviceSyuruiCode" = A."dbT3033KyufujissekiShukei_serviceSyuruiCode" AND DbT3033KyufujissekiShukei."jigyoshoNo" = A."dbT3033KyufujissekiShukei_jigyoshoNo" AND DbT3033KyufujissekiShukei."seiriNo" = A."dbT3033KyufujissekiShukei_seiriNo") ORDER BY A."dbT3033KyufujissekiShukei_serviceTeikyoYM" DESC, A."dbT3033KyufujissekiShukei_inputShikibetsuNo", A."dbT3033KyufujissekiShukei_serviceSyuruiCode", A."dbT3033KyufujissekiShukei_jigyoshoNo", A."dbT3033KyufujissekiShukei_seiriNo" DESC
